'From Squeak3.6gamma of ''11 September 2003'' [latest update: #5420] on 17 September 2003 at 12:05:12 am'!"Change Set:		DeprecationPreference-aviDate:			16 September 2003Author:			Avi BryantAdds a preference to control whether or not to show warnings for deprecated methods.  The preference is off by default.  (added deprecatedExplanation: implementation -dew)"!!Object methodsFor: 'error handling' stamp: 'avi 9/16/2003 11:44'!deprecated: aBlock explanation: aString 	 "Warn that the sender has been deprecated. answer the value of aBlock on resumption"	Preferences showDeprecationWarnings ifTrue:		[Deprecation			signal: thisContext sender printString, ' has been deprecated. ', aString].	^ aBlock value.! !!Object methodsFor: 'error handling' stamp: 'dew 9/17/2003 00:02'!deprecatedExplanation: aString	"Warn that the sending method has been deprecated"	Preferences showDeprecationWarnings ifTrue:		[Deprecation signal: thisContext sender printString, ' has been deprecated. ', aString]! !!Preferences class methodsFor: 'standard queries'!showDeprecationWarnings	^ self		valueOfFlag: #showDeprecationWarnings		ifAbsent: [false]! !"Postscript:Add the #showDeprecationWarnings preference"Preferences addPreference: #showDeprecationWarnings category: #debug default: false balloonHelp: 'Warn the user when a deprecated method is used.'.!